---
---
<div class="space-y-14">
  <div>
    <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-steel uppercase mb-3">Services</p>
    <h2 class="text-[1.75rem] lg:text-[2rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-3 leading-tight">
      One engagement. Three phases. Your operation, fully transferred.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-slate text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      We step in as interim Managing Director, build and stabilize your Romania office, then hire and onboard your permanent local leader. You get executive-grade operations from day one — and full ownership when you are ready.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-surface border border-divider rounded-md p-8 space-y-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="relative">
        <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] text-steel uppercase mb-2">Phase 1</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Build</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.8125rem] text-steel mb-2">4–8 weeks</p>
        <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-slate leading-relaxed">Legal entity and vendor setup, recruiting pipeline and first hires, onboarding playbook, operating baseline established.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] text-steel uppercase mb-2">Phase 2</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Operate</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.8125rem] text-steel mb-2">3–18 months</p>
        <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-slate leading-relaxed">Interim MD runs daily operations: delivery governance, KPI cadence, budget control, team growth, risk and escalation management.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] text-steel uppercase mb-2">Phase 3</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Transfer</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.8125rem] text-steel mb-2">Structured handover</p>
        <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-slate leading-relaxed">We recruit and mentor your permanent local leader. Structured handover playbook, knowledge transfer, and clean operational transition.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-5 border-t border-divider">
      <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] text-steel uppercase mb-3">Included across all phases</p>
      <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-2.5 text-slate text-[0.875rem] leading-relaxed">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-foreground mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">&rarr;</span> Executive rhythm: KPIs, meeting cadence, decision discipline</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-foreground mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">&rarr;</span> Recruiting engine: scorecards, sourcing, structured interviews</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-foreground mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">&rarr;</span> Delivery governance: priorities, risks, escalation, stakeholder reporting</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-foreground mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">&rarr;</span> Budget and cost control: transparent reporting, vendor management</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-foreground mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">&rarr;</span> AI-assisted operations: faster recruiting, clearer reporting, lower overhead</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-foreground mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">&rarr;</span> Leadership transition: hire, mentor, and onboard your permanent MD</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-steel-light border border-divider rounded-md p-6">
    <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] text-steel uppercase mb-2">Flexible engagement</p>
    <p class="text-slate text-[0.875rem] leading-relaxed">
      Already have a Romania team that needs stabilization? We can start at Phase 2 (Operate) and focus on governance, delivery, and leadership development — without the build phase.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
